register.name: ICTR
register.description: Provides information about the interrupt controller

bitField.name: INTLINESNUM
bitField.description: The total number of interrupt lines supported n, defined in groups of 32. That is, the total number of interrupt lines is up to (32*(INTLINESNUM+1)). However, the absolute maximum number of interrupts is 496, corresponding to the INTLINESNUM value 0b1111.
